        <updateDate>2019-08-09T15:18:25Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Energy Jobs for our Heroes Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill establishes the Energy-Ready Vets Program within the Department of Energy. The program must prepare eligible veterans for careers in the energy industry.</p>]]></text>
